{
  "conversations": [
    {
      "conversationId": "scene_0",
      "lines": [
        {
          "text": "You're awake earlier than usual.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "I couldn't sleep.",
          "characterId": "marina",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "a moment of silence where we can see Marina's discomfort",
          "characterId": "narration",
          "emotion": "default",
          "enterSide": 2
        },
        {
          "text": "....",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Does it hurt ?",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "...",
          "characterId": "marina",
          "emotion": "sick",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "You can tell me if it does.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "I know...",
          "characterId": "marina",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Don't worry. I'll make sure you get better.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "maybe a short cutscene without dialogues where Aldric gets up or walks somewhere to get us to the portal scene",
          "characterId": "narration",
          "emotion": "default",
          "enterSide": 2
        },
        {
          "text": "when portal appears",
          "characterId": "narration",
          "emotion": "default",
          "enterSide": 2
        },
        {
          "text": "What is this?!",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "What is happening?!",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Marina ! reaching out for her",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Dad ! Wait, no !",
          "characterId": "marina",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "intro",
      "lines": [
        {
          "text": "What happened? Where am I?",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "I need to get back to Marina !",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "siren humming voices",
          "characterId": "narration",
          "emotion": "default",
          "enterSide": 2
        },
        {
          "text": "Huh? What is that sound ?",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "It sounds heavenly...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Almost like...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Lyralei appears",
          "characterId": "narration",
          "emotion": "default",
          "enterSide": 2
        },
        {
          "text": "You don't belong here... do you?",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "What the- How'd you- Who are you?!",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "I am Lyralei. And you're...",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "I need to go back to my daughter!",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Your... daughter?",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Yes ! I can't leave her alone...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "You're holding onto her very tightly...",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Yes... After all... she's...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Hm?",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Nothing...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "You still haven't told me your name.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Aldric.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Do you know why you were brought here, Aldric ?",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "I don't care why! Send me back!",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "I am not the one who brought you here.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "But I can help you get back to your daughter.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Now tell me about her.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Marina... My daughter...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "She's very sick.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Sick, you say?",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Void Sickness. It's a sickness that slowly drains her life force.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Hmm... I've heard about that...",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "She can't be left alone.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Alone?",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "My wife... She-",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "I'm... I'm all Marina has.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "I see...",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Then we shouldn't keep her waiting.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Yes ! Please !",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Getting back to her is possible. And her illness... can be touched.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Now. This place doesn't take people without reason.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "And I will guide you throughout this adventure. So listen carefully.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "We need to gather three portal fragments and then you can go back to your daughter using them.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "world_1",
      "lines": [
        {
          "text": "This journey will take us to three different dimensions, this being the first one.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "You will face different obstacles in every dimension.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "This is The Shattered Calm.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "The Shattered Calm?",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Yes. We will need the Compass Shard, which is embedded in the eye of the giant statue on the floating island, to get out of this dimension.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "To get the fragment, you will have to solve a puzzle while avoiding getting caught by the eye's sight.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "But first...",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "you need to beat the kraken, which will be your first obstacle.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "THE WHAT?",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "The Mirage Kraken. A massive translucent squid that shifts between dimensions",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "I'm only a retired sailor! How am I supposed to beat that thing!",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Now, now... Calm down...",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Stay with me and you'll make it through. I know you will.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "at the end",
          "characterId": "narration",
          "emotion": "default",
          "enterSide": 2
        },
        {
          "text": "Now. This fragment will allow us navigate between dimensional boundaries.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "world_2",
      "lines": [
        {
          "text": "I knew you could do it! You see? You're stronger than you think.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "But that was only the first step. Come now... we're not done yet.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Woah... What is this place...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "This is The Icy Shores.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "We will need a fragment to get out of this place as well. The Eternal Ice.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "To get to the Eternal Ice, you will have to sneak through the palace while the Frost Empress is sleeping, using your Storm Core power to melt ice barriers.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "But first-",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Let me guess. I have to fight a giant snowman.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Well... Something like that…",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Really? It'll be a piece of cake then.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Not really.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Icy Man was once the Frost Empress's greatest warrior but he was cursed into an eternal, mindless guardian after failing to break her spell of endless winter.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Well, I'd be surprised.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "This is not an easy road, Aldric. But I know you will make it.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "I have to... for my-",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Daughter. I know. Now go...",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Uhh, okay...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "2nd world end",
          "characterId": "narration",
          "emotion": "default",
          "enterSide": 2
        },
        {
          "text": "The Eternal Ice's power is to freeze dimensional barriers to make them solid and croassable.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "world_3",
      "lines": [
        {
          "text": "*sigh* That was... something...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "You're getting the hang of this.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "....Yeah. I guess I am.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "I'll admit... I didn't expect us to make it out of even the first world.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "But you sai-",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "But now... You seem to have it under control.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Heh... I'm starting to feel that way too.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Then perhaps... I'm no longer needed?",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "WHAT? NO!",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Hm... so you do rely on me.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "That's not what I-",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Relax. I'm only teasing. You gullible old man...",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Hey! I'm not that old!",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "So you accept that you're gullible?",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Wha- NO!",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "You're impossible.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "I know.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "I like tha-",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "We need to hurry up. We are close to getting you back to your daughter.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "This is The Mistland-",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "I already know... I have to beat a monster to get the fragment.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Yes, indeed.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "You will fight The Imitator Angler. And to get the The Truth Prism, the fragment, you must trick the Angler into revealing its true form, and strike at the exact moment the prism is exposed.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "That sounds easier than the last two.",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Say... Do you MAYBE want to help me this time?",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "I...",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Uhh...",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "I- I have to protect you from a distance.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Well... Okay then...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "end_of_world_3_boss_fight",
      "lines": [
        {
          "text": "ALDRIC!! We made it! I can't believe!",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Yeah... well, I did most of the-",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Finally.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "You've done well.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "\"Done well\"? That's it?",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Hush.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Listen carefully now.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "...?",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "I've been waiting for this moment... for longer than you can imagine.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "The fragments you gathered-",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "The fragments?",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Do not interrupt me.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "...?",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "The fragments that you've gathered... They were never for you.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "...What?",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "They are the key to my freedom.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "The Void Depths... my prison.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Prison? What are you talking about?",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "But what about Mari-",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Marina? You really are a gullible old man, aren't you!",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "You really believed I cared about her.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Everything I told you... Every step...",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "It was all to lead you here.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "scary",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "And now... you've brought me exactly what I needed.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "Lyralei...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
          "enterSide": 1
        },
        {
          "text": "Don't look so surprised.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "You were useful. That's all.",
          "characterId": "siren",
          "emotion": "angry",
          "enterSide": 0
        },
        {
          "text": "...",
          "characterId": "aldric",
          "emotion": "sad",
